0.001003 2026-07-16
    - Store payloads as SQLite BLOBs and read ranges by byte offset.

0.001002 2026-07-13
    - Separate metadata and blob-byte storage behind public component APIs.
    - Migrate the 0.001000 and 0.001001 combined schemas automatically while
      preserving data.
    - Roll back the migration when legacy owner relationships are invalid.
    - Reject metadata changes, blob preparation, and blob deletion outside the
      coordinating transaction.

0.001001 2026-07-13
    - Use Class::Tiny for all object construction.
    - Reject DBI handles with AutoCommit disabled.
    - Ensure coverage tests load the working-tree module.

0.001000 2026-07-09
    - Initial CPAN release.
